SELECT *
FROM (
	SELECT DISTINCT T.ID, T.DESCRIPTION, T.DEL_FLAG, T.UPDATE_TIM E, TD.NAME AS DNAME
		, TDR.NAME AS RNAME, ROWNUM AS rn
	FROM T_DGAP_ALERT_CONFIG T
	LEFT JOIN T_DGAP_RESOURCE TD ON T.TARGET_ID = TD.ID 
		LEFT JOIN T_DGAP_RESOURCE_DIRECTORY TDR ON TD.DIRECTORY_ID = TDR.ID 
	WHERE 1 = 1
		A ND T.DEL_FLAG = ?
	ORDER BY T.UPDATE_TIME DESC
)
WHERE rn BETWEEN ? + ? * (? - ?) AND ? * ?;

SELECT *
FROM T_DGAP_RESOURCE_DIRECTORY T
WHERE T.DEL_FLAG = ?
ORDER BY T.UPDATE_TIME DESC;

SELE CT COUNT(*)
FROM T_DGAP_ALERT_CONFIG T
WHERE 1 = 1
	AND T.DEL_FLAG = ?;
